data.description: Welcome to this LUXURIOUS POOL HOME located on a cul-de-sac corner lot in the gated Fish Hawk Trails! This home has been so well maintained and loaded with upgrades! A few of the upgrades include a NEW hot water heater in 2021, wood-look ceramic tile flooring throughout the living areas, interior and exterior paint, a Reverse Osmosis System, and so much more that you just have to see for yourself! The curb appeal is second to none with stacked stone accents, side entry 3-car garage, meticulous landscaping, and a charming front porch to enjoy your morning coffee! Once you step through the double leaded glass front door you will appreciate the circular foyer with upgraded chandelier that welcomes you inside! This unique floor plan boasts luxury and functionally at the same time offering an open concept AND a triple split floor plan! Behind a set of French doors there is a private home office, so working from home will be a treat! The formal dining room features tray ceiling with crown and views of the sparkling pool and spa! Across from the dining room is the formal living room; entertaining family and friends will be a breeze! Pass the butler’s pantry and discover the heart of the home, the A M A Z I N G kitchen! The chef in the family will appreciate this kitchen from the moment they step into this room! Featuring an abundance of 42-in wood cabinets, center island, breakfast bar seating, built-in double oven, and a bright and open breakfast nook for everyday meals! Memories were meant to be made in the spacious family room with a gas-burning fireplace and built-ins for extra storage! The LARGE master suite is every parents’ oasis featuring crown molding, his and hers walk-in closets, a spa-like en-suite with separate vanities, upgraded lighting, soaking tub, separate walk-in shower, and an attached room perfect for a second private office, workout room, or great nursery space for new parents! Two additional roomy bedrooms share a jack and jill bathroom while the fourth bedroom has a 3rd full bathroom nearby at the back of the home near the HUGE bonus room! With vaulted ceilings and plenty of windows, this bright space allows you to be able to store the kids' toys away from the living areas with ease! High ceilings, neutral paint, and wide baseboards complete this perfect home that is calling your name! The screened and freshly painted lanai features a glistening pool and spa so summer days will be spent out here all day, every day! Take a dip and enjoy the Florida weather and grill out on your outdoor kitchen! The backyard offers plenty of space to run and play so the kids and pets will be so happy! Enjoy peace of mind knowing that there is a backup generator in case of emergency! Fish Hawk Trails is the place to be; Guard gated, community park and tennis courts, and zoned for some of the best schools in the county! Start packing, you won't find a home better than this one!
